# The Biblical Track Record: Characteristics First, Names Later

## How God's Prophetic Methodology Works in Demonstrable History

---

## Purpose of This Document

This document demonstrates that the characteristics-based methodology of biblical prophecy **works**. Before events occurred, God gave descriptive markers through His prophets. When the events unfolded, the names and specifics were revealed — and they matched the characteristics precisely.

This is not theory. This is the **biblical track record** — prophecy after prophecy, verified by Scripture itself.

**Amos 3:7** — *"Surely the Lord GOD will do nothing, but he revealeth his secret unto his servants the prophets."*

What follows is the evidence: characteristics given, fulfillment documented, names revealed.

